modShortDescription: This mod will expand the building process. The health of the blocks will also be changed.
modDescription:
This mod will expand the building process.

**Building process will look like this:** Wood => Reinforced Wood => Reinforced Metal Wood => Cobblestone => Concrete => Concrete Reinforced => Steel

The health of the blocks will also be changed.

**[Download](https://drive.google.com/file/d/11wvrFXlodS9q6RiUVhPZSSdtwqv0e0K7/view?usp=sharing)**
